deleverageAccount(address,address,addres.notice: If an account is below the minimum collateral ratio, this method wil deleverage (liquidate) that account. `depositAmountPrimeCash` in the borrow currency will be transferred from the liquidator and used to offset the account's debt position. params.account: the address that will exit the vault
